## ğŸš€ Overview  
`havinosh_data_loader` is a powerful Python package designed to **automatically detect CSV structure**, **create tables**, and **insert data into PostgreSQL** with minimal effort.  
Simply drop your CSV files into a folder, and `havinosh_data_loader` will handle everything dynamically.  

---

## ğŸ“Œ Features  
âœ… **Automatic Table Creation** â€“ Reads CSV headers and maps them to PostgreSQL columns  
âœ… **Dynamic Schema Detection** â€“ Infers data types automatically  
âœ… **Batch Data Insertion** â€“ Efficiently loads large datasets  
âœ… **Error Handling** â€“ Logs errors and provides detailed debugging  
âœ… **Environment Configuration** â€“ Uses `.env` file for database credentials  
âœ… **Modular & Extensible** â€“ Well-structured for easy modifications  

